trans-unit.source: A service contract that defines the methods that wrap the Message-oriented operation contracts exposed by IWSTrustChannelContract.
Asynchronously sends a WS-Trust Cancel message to an endpoint.
The <xref href="System.IdentityModel.Protocols.WSTrust.RequestSecurityToken"></xref> that represents the request to the STS.
An optional <xref:System.AsyncCallback> delegate, to be called when the send is complete.
A user-provided object that distinguishes this particular asynchronous send request from other requests.
An <xref:System.IAsyncResult> object that represents the asynchronous send, which could still be pending.
